00:39.539 --> 00:48.131
♪ ♪

00:54.554 --> 00:57.515
[bones cracking]

01:01.060 --> 01:04.480
- DON'T TRY TO CARRY
TOO MANY BOXES, BESSIE.

01:04.563 --> 01:05.815
YOU DON'T HAVE
THE HEAVY LIFTING BADGE YET.

01:05.899 --> 01:08.067
- DON'T WORRY, MRS. GIBBONS.

01:08.151 --> 01:09.819
BADGE AND TASK
ARE BOTH IN SIGHT.

01:09.903 --> 01:12.238
PLUS, I'VE GOT A SPOTTER.

01:12.322 --> 01:14.282
REMEMBER, FINGER,
LIFT WITH YOUR KNUCKLE.

01:15.408 --> 01:19.120
[grunting]

01:22.749 --> 01:25.710
[screaming]

01:27.629 --> 01:29.798
[sighs]

01:29.881 --> 01:30.757
crash!

01:30.840 --> 01:32.675
[all gasping]

01:32.759 --> 01:34.302
- BESSIE HIGGENBOTTOM!

01:34.385 --> 01:37.680
DID I NOT SPECIFICALLY TELL YOU
NOT TO CARRY THAT MANY BOXES?

01:37.764 --> 01:40.600
ALL THIS TAFFY IS RUINED!

01:40.683 --> 01:44.771
THESE ARE TINY PIECES
OF PROFIT IN THE MUD.

01:44.854 --> 01:46.356
- ITS OKAY, MRS. GIBBONS.

01:46.439 --> 01:48.650
ONE WASH CYCLE
AND THESE'LL BE GOOD AS NEW!

01:48.733 --> 01:49.609
JUST WATCH!

01:49.692 --> 01:52.529
[water sloshing]

01:52.612 --> 01:54.697
- I HEREBY ISSUE YOU

01:54.781 --> 01:57.200
A BEE-MERIT!

01:57.283 --> 01:58.368
- A B-B-B-B-BEE MERIT?

01:58.451 --> 01:58.868
BUT--

01:58.952 --> 02:00.370
[paper ripping]

02:00.453 --> 02:00.870
- HERE!

02:00.954 --> 02:03.581
ACCEPT THE SHAME.

02:03.665 --> 02:05.875
- BUT MRS. GIBBONS,

02:05.959 --> 02:08.044
I'VE NEVER RECEIVED
A BEE-MERIT BEFORE.

02:08.127 --> 02:11.256
I WAS ONLY FOLLOWING
ORDERS BETTER AND FASTER.

02:11.339 --> 02:11.381
PLEASE!

02:15.885 --> 02:16.803
N-NO!

02:16.886 --> 02:17.762
N-N-NO!

02:17.846 --> 02:18.805
OH, OH, IT BURNS!

02:18.888 --> 02:21.099
IT BURNS, OH, IT BURNS!

02:21.182 --> 02:23.810
- WELL, CLEAN THIS UP
WHEN YOU'RE DONE WITH THAT.

02:26.020 --> 02:27.272
- [sighs]

02:27.355 --> 02:29.274
NEVER IN MY ENTIRE CAREER
AS A HONEYBEE HAVE I EVER

02:29.357 --> 02:30.942
RECEIVED A BEE-MERIT.

02:31.025 --> 02:33.111
MY RECORD WAS SO CLEAN
YOU COULD EAT OFF OF IT.

02:33.194 --> 02:36.239
YOU COULD WIPE A BABY'S FACE
WITH MY RECORD.

02:36.322 --> 02:37.073
YOU COULD FALL INTO MY RECORD

02:37.156 --> 02:39.951
LIKE IT WAS A PILE
OF FRESH LAUNDRY.

02:40.034 --> 02:41.244
- UH-HUH.

02:41.327 --> 02:42.412
- EVEN IF I'M PERFECT

02:42.495 --> 02:43.079
FOR THE REST
OF MY HONEYBEE CAREER--

02:43.162 --> 02:44.205
WHICH I WAS PLANNING TO BE--

02:44.289 --> 02:48.835
MY RECORD WILL NEVER BE PERFECT
EVER AGAIN, EVER!

02:48.918 --> 02:51.045
IT IS BESMIRCHED!

02:51.129 --> 02:52.755
OH, WHAT'S THE POINT OF BEING
GOOD FROM NOW ON?

02:52.839 --> 02:55.842
I MEAN, WHO CARES?

02:55.925 --> 02:57.302
[thunder crashes]

02:57.385 --> 02:59.762
- [growling and snorting]

02:59.846 --> 03:01.222
- I KNOW, I KNOW.

03:01.306 --> 03:04.809
HAPPY, YOU'RE PREACHING KETCHUP
TO A FRENCH FRY.

03:09.314 --> 03:11.900
- BESSIE, YOU WANT ME TO RETURN
YOUR LIBRARY BOOKS?

03:11.983 --> 03:13.401
THEY'RE DUE AT 3:00.

03:13.484 --> 03:14.277
- I KNOW WHEN THEY'RE DUE, BEN.

03:14.360 --> 03:16.613
THEY'RE RIGHT HERE,
ALL READY TO--

03:16.696 --> 03:18.615
YOU KNOW WHAT?

03:18.698 --> 03:21.326
WHO CARES?

03:21.409 --> 03:24.037
I'LL RETURN THEM
WHEN I FEEL LIKE IT.

03:24.120 --> 03:27.832
MAYBE AT 4:15!

03:27.916 --> 03:28.833
- [gasps]

03:28.917 --> 03:30.043
YOU'LL INCUR LATE FEES!

03:30.126 --> 03:30.793
SO WHAT?

03:30.877 --> 03:31.794
LET 'EM BILL ME!

03:31.878 --> 03:35.214
- YOU'RE NOT MY SISTER.

03:35.298 --> 03:36.883
[zipper sliding]

03:36.966 --> 03:39.969
[bluesy rock music]

03:40.053 --> 03:41.721
♪ ♪

03:41.804 --> 03:43.014
- [growls]

03:43.097 --> 03:44.849
- YOU GOT THAT RIGHT, HAPS.

03:44.933 --> 03:47.769
TREAT YOUR EYEBALLS
TO A WHOLE NEW BESSIE.

03:47.852 --> 03:51.606
[thunder crashes]

03:57.737 --> 03:58.988
- [barking madly]

03:59.072 --> 04:00.156
- HAPPY, HEEL!

04:00.239 --> 04:03.117
WAIT, I MEAN, DON'T HEEL.

04:03.201 --> 04:04.702
BARK LOUDER!

04:04.786 --> 04:07.830
[savage barking]

04:07.914 --> 04:09.707
- [loud barking]

04:09.791 --> 04:12.043
- YEAH, GOOD BOY!

04:12.126 --> 04:13.711
I MEAN, BAD BOY!

04:13.795 --> 04:15.254
GOOD BAD BOY!

04:16.839 --> 04:18.466
I AIN'T GOT TIME TO SMELL YA'S.

04:20.718 --> 04:23.137
- OH.

04:23.221 --> 04:25.682
- NO THANK YOU.

04:25.765 --> 04:26.975
- [scoffs]

04:27.058 --> 04:28.935
- MAY I HAVE YOUR CLAIM TICKET?

04:29.018 --> 04:29.894
- GUESS WHAT?

04:29.978 --> 04:31.479
I DIDN'T BRING MY TICKET.

04:31.562 --> 04:35.692
SO YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO SEARCH BY MY LAST NAME.

04:36.985 --> 04:38.861
IT'S HIGGENBOTTOM.

04:38.945 --> 04:42.532
SEE IF YOU CAN SPELL IT.

04:46.160 --> 04:49.122
I'M TAKING TWO PENNIES.

04:49.205 --> 04:51.791
WHO CARES?

04:51.874 --> 04:54.544
INSIDE THE LINES,
OUTSIDE THE LINES:

04:54.627 --> 04:55.378
WHO CARES?

04:58.089 --> 05:00.925
- [screams]

05:03.845 --> 05:05.054
- UP, DOWN?

05:05.138 --> 05:08.641
THOSE ARE JUST SIGNS.

05:08.725 --> 05:11.477
WHO CARES?

05:11.561 --> 05:12.687
HORRIBLE PAIN.

05:12.770 --> 05:16.983
WHO CARES?

05:20.069 --> 05:22.447
WHO CARES?

05:22.530 --> 05:24.073
[gasping and squeaking]

05:24.157 --> 05:25.199
- YEAH, AND THEN I SAID,

05:25.283 --> 05:26.701
"IF YOU'RE SO SMART,

05:26.784 --> 05:29.328
WHY DID YOU SPELL 'AMBULANCE'
BACKWARDS ON YOUR CAR?"

05:29.412 --> 05:32.123
- ISN'T THAT SO YOU CAN READ IT
IN YOUR REARVIEW MIRROR?

05:32.206 --> 05:36.294
- UGH, HE TRIED TO SAY
THE SAME THING.

05:36.377 --> 05:40.715
HEY, YOU AND YOUR PLEATHER
JACKET BUMPED MY SEAT.

05:42.008 --> 05:45.053
- WHO CARES?

05:45.136 --> 05:46.721
[both gasp]

05:48.347 --> 05:50.725
[roars]

05:50.808 --> 05:51.309
- MESSIE?

05:51.392 --> 05:52.769
- YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT.

05:52.852 --> 05:54.228
I'M A MESS.

05:54.312 --> 05:56.689
WHO CARES?

05:56.773 --> 05:59.525
- I, LIKE, CANT BELIEVE
I'M SAYING THIS AND STUFF,

05:59.609 --> 06:02.570
BUT SUDDENLY YOU SEEM SEMI-COOL?

06:02.653 --> 06:03.488
SO GWEN AND I WERE,
LIKE, WONDERING

06:03.571 --> 06:05.865
IF YOU MAYBE WANNA
GO SWIMMING WITH US?

06:05.948 --> 06:08.534
- EH, SWIMMING'S FOR SQUARES.

06:08.618 --> 06:09.619
- OH, YEAH, TOTES.

06:09.702 --> 06:10.620
- BUT OKAY.

06:10.703 --> 06:11.412
BUT WHO CARES?

06:14.457 --> 06:18.628
- SO, MESS, WHAT ELSE DO YOU
NOT CARE ABOUT?

06:18.711 --> 06:21.589
BECAUSE I BARELY CARE
ABOUT ANYTHING.

06:21.672 --> 06:25.593
- BIRTHDAYS, BUNNIES, COOKIES,
FABRIC SOFTENER,

06:25.676 --> 06:27.887
HISTORY, FLUSHING THE TOILET.

06:27.970 --> 06:30.973
- YEAH, COOL, WE DON'T CARE
ABOUT THAT STUFF EITHER.

06:31.057 --> 06:31.849
MAYBE THE TOILET.

06:31.933 --> 06:33.976
- ADULT SWIM!

06:34.060 --> 06:35.436
ALL KIDS OUT OF THE POOL!

06:35.520 --> 06:36.771
ADULT SWIM!

06:36.854 --> 06:39.774
[kids groan]

06:43.611 --> 06:44.821
[both gasp]

06:44.904 --> 06:46.656
HEY, YOU!

06:46.739 --> 06:47.115
GET OUT OF THERE!

06:47.198 --> 06:49.867
IT'S ADULT SWIM!

06:53.788 --> 06:54.789
- WHO CARES?

06:54.872 --> 06:59.085
- WO-OW.

07:01.045 --> 07:02.588
- WHAT'S UP, BADNESS?

07:02.672 --> 07:04.215
WANNA WALK INTO THE MEETING
WITH US?

07:04.298 --> 07:05.466
- NO CAN DO.

07:05.550 --> 07:09.220
I THINK I'M GONNA BE
FIVE MINUTES LATE TODAY.

07:09.303 --> 07:12.431
- OH, WE WOULD TOTALLY
DO THAT TOO,

07:12.515 --> 07:15.017
BUT, YOU KNOW, MY MOM PAYS ME
TO MAKE CAMEOS.

07:15.101 --> 07:17.687
WE'LL SAVE YOU A SEAT.

07:17.770 --> 07:18.688
- WHATEVER.

07:18.771 --> 07:19.105
I'LL SIT ON THE FLOOR.

07:19.188 --> 07:22.525
WHO CARES?

07:22.608 --> 07:25.111
- I CANNOT STRESS
HOW IMPORTANT IT IS

07:25.194 --> 07:26.821
THAT WE CORRECTLY REPORT

07:26.904 --> 07:29.824
HOW MANY BOXES OF TAFFY
BESSIE HAS RUINED,

07:29.907 --> 07:33.035
NOT ONLY TO REMIND BESSIE
OF HER HUGE ERROR,

07:33.119 --> 07:35.413
BUT ALSO TO ENSURE
THAT HONEYBEE H.Q.

07:35.496 --> 07:37.790
SENDS US THE RIGHT NUMBER
OF REPLACEMENT BOXES.

07:37.874 --> 07:42.378
ding!

07:42.461 --> 07:45.423
[laughter]

07:46.716 --> 07:48.050
- YEAH, JUST IN TIME TO BE LATE.

07:48.134 --> 07:50.094
COME ON, HAPS.

07:50.178 --> 07:53.431
- BESSIE,
WE HAVE A BAD-TASTIC PLAN.

07:53.514 --> 07:54.432
GET OVER HERE.

07:54.515 --> 07:55.892
- SWEET.

07:55.975 --> 07:59.729
- I GOT MY MOMS KEYS SO WE CAN
EACH TAKE ONE BOX OF TAFFY

07:59.812 --> 08:01.397
OUT OF THE STORAGE CLOSET.

08:01.480 --> 08:04.817
THEN I'LL TELL MY MOM
THEY WERE DAMAGED.

08:04.901 --> 08:06.319
SHE WRITES IT INTO HER REPORT

08:06.402 --> 08:09.071
AND STILL GETS
REPLACEMENT BOXES FOR THEM.

08:09.155 --> 08:10.156
HA!

08:10.239 --> 08:11.073
CALM DOWN.

08:11.157 --> 08:14.118
I KNOW IT'S GENIUS.

08:15.536 --> 08:18.539
[triumphant music]

08:18.623 --> 08:19.790
♪ ♪

08:19.874 --> 08:23.586
- NOTHING TASTES BETTER
THAN STOLEN TAFFY, RIGHT?

08:23.669 --> 08:25.796
- STEAL TAFFY?

08:28.925 --> 08:30.468
- AH, AH, AH.

08:30.551 --> 08:32.803
LOOKOUTS
LOOK AND STAY OUT.

08:32.886 --> 08:35.014
[door slams]

08:35.097 --> 08:36.474
- [grumbling]

08:36.557 --> 08:38.142
- WHOA.

08:38.226 --> 08:40.311
I'VE NEVER FELT SO SMALL.

08:40.394 --> 08:42.520
- I'M GOING FOR VINTAGE,
ONE OF THE EXPENSIVE YEARS.

08:42.605 --> 08:45.566
- UM, I'M JUST GONNA
TAKE THIS LITTLE BOX.

08:45.650 --> 08:48.653
IT'S GOT A DENT IN IT,
SO IT'S PROBABLY AGAINST

08:48.736 --> 08:51.489
FDA REGULATIONS
TO SELL IT ANYWAY.

08:51.572 --> 08:52.949
BUT I'M STILL STEALING IT.

08:58.371 --> 08:59.664
- [pounding on door]

08:59.747 --> 09:01.749
[angry barking]

09:01.832 --> 09:03.125
- UGH, DOG MINUTES?

09:03.209 --> 09:04.126
PLEASE.

09:04.210 --> 09:06.170
WE'RE ALMOST DONE.

09:06.254 --> 09:10.007
- PTHHBT.

09:15.471 --> 09:16.931
[all gasp]

09:22.228 --> 09:24.814
[both chomping]

09:24.897 --> 09:26.899
[laughs]

09:26.983 --> 09:28.067
- THIS IS SO GETTING
ITS OWN CHAPTER

09:28.150 --> 09:29.068
IN MY MEMOIRS!

09:29.151 --> 09:29.819
[laughs]

09:29.902 --> 09:31.028
- THAT WAS SUPER GREAT, GUYS.

09:31.112 --> 09:32.363
- COME ON, MESSIE.

09:32.446 --> 09:34.407
AREN'T YOU GONNA EAT YOURS?

09:34.490 --> 09:36.492
- OH, YEAH, TOTALLY.

09:36.575 --> 09:39.954
I-I CANT WAIT TO BITE
INTO THIS DELICIOUS TAFFY.

09:40.037 --> 09:42.373
- WHO CARES, RIGHT?

09:42.456 --> 09:42.790
- RIGHT.

09:44.083 --> 09:45.960
HERE GOES.

09:47.169 --> 09:50.172
[gagging]

09:57.763 --> 09:59.098
OH, NO, SOMETHING'S COMIN' UP!

09:59.181 --> 10:01.559
[heavy breathing]

10:01.642 --> 10:02.852
I KNOW STEALING IS WRONG.

10:02.935 --> 10:04.312
WHO CARES?

10:04.395 --> 10:05.187
A HONEYBEE SWEARS
TO MAINTAIN HONESTY

10:05.271 --> 10:07.440
AND INTEGRITY AT ALL TIMES.

10:07.523 --> 10:08.524
WHO CARES?

10:08.607 --> 10:09.525
I'VE CROSSED A LINE

10:09.608 --> 10:11.277
THAT I CAN NEVER RETURN FROM!

10:11.360 --> 10:12.236
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

10:12.320 --> 10:13.529
YOU CAN ALWAYS COME BACK.

10:13.612 --> 10:15.323
WHO SAYS I EVEN WANNA GO BACK?

10:15.406 --> 10:17.616
MAYBE THE TAFFY'S CHEWIER
ON THE OTHER SIDE.

10:17.700 --> 10:18.701
YOU EVER THOUGHT OF THAT?

10:18.784 --> 10:19.243
BUT WHAT ABOUT THE LINE?

10:19.327 --> 10:20.620
YOU CAN STEP OVER IT

10:20.703 --> 10:23.164
WITHOUT TECHNICALLY
STEPPING ON IT.

10:23.247 --> 10:24.665
BUT I'M AN EXCELLENT HONEYBEE,

10:24.749 --> 10:26.375
HOWEVER IMPERFECT MY RECORD
MAY BE.

10:26.459 --> 10:28.878
WHO CARES?

10:28.961 --> 10:31.005
I CARES!

10:31.088 --> 10:32.089
[toilet flushing]

10:32.173 --> 10:34.050
- OW!

10:34.133 --> 10:37.720
- IT'S NOT ABOUT PERFECT RECORDS
AND ZERO BEE-MERITS.

10:37.803 --> 10:38.804
BEING GOOD IS WHAT
A HONEYBEE DOES.

10:41.140 --> 10:43.351
AND A HONEYBEE DOES NOT STEAL.

10:47.688 --> 10:50.066
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

10:50.149 --> 10:51.567
I THOUGHT YOU WERE, LIKE, BAD!

10:51.650 --> 10:52.401
- WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU?

10:52.485 --> 10:55.738
- IT'S WHAT'S RIGHT WITH ME.

10:57.114 --> 10:59.283
- GIRLS?

11:02.787 --> 11:03.746
- OH MRS. GIBBONS,
THERE YOU ARE.

11:03.829 --> 11:07.333
I AM IN DIRE NEED
OF HARD LABOR AS REDEMPTION.

11:07.416 --> 11:10.211
I VOLUNTEER MYSELF FOR BATHROOM
CLEAN-UP DUTY,

11:10.294 --> 11:12.755
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY!

11:12.838 --> 11:14.048
- BE MY GUEST.

11:14.131 --> 11:16.717
I'M NOT TIPPING YOU.

11:16.801 --> 11:20.096
[scrubbing noises]

11:20.179 --> 11:25.476
AH, GOOD TO SEE YOU AGAIN,
OLD FRIEND.

11:25.559 --> 11:29.397
- [belching]

11:29.480 --> 11:30.481
- [gasps]

11:32.566 --> 11:33.943
HAPPY.

11:36.737 --> 11:39.782
[eerie music]

11:39.865 --> 11:45.704
♪ ♪

11:45.788 --> 11:47.123
[bees buzzing]

11:47.206 --> 11:48.624
- THERE THEY ARE, MOMMY!

11:48.707 --> 11:49.542
THEY RUINED MY PAGEANT FACE!

11:49.625 --> 11:52.086
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO WIN
A PAGEANT NOW?

11:52.169 --> 11:53.921
WITH MY PERSONALITY?

11:54.004 --> 11:56.882
- NOBODY RUINS
OUR WINNING STREAK.

11:56.966 --> 11:57.883
[clicking]

11:57.967 --> 11:59.468
- NO!

11:59.552 --> 12:02.596
FOR THE LOVE OF HONEY, STOP!

12:03.597 --> 12:04.640
MRS. GIBBONS,

12:04.723 --> 12:06.559
YOU NEARLY ACCIDENTALLY
EXTERMINATED

12:06.642 --> 12:08.144
THE SACRED SYMBOL
OF THE HONEYBEES:

12:08.227 --> 12:10.938
HONEYBEES!

12:11.021 --> 12:14.817
- BESSIE, IT IS A SIMPLE MATTER
OF SAFETY AND REVENGE.

12:14.900 --> 12:17.820
JUST LOOK AT WHAT THEY DID
TO <i> MON PETITE PORTIA.</i>

12:19.405 --> 12:21.323
IF YOU CAN THINK
OF A DEATHLESS SOLUTION,

12:21.407 --> 12:22.616
BE MY GUEST.

12:24.076 --> 12:28.038
- DEATHLESS SOLUTION,
DEATHLESS SOLUTION.

12:28.122 --> 12:28.456
[bees buzzing]

12:28.539 --> 12:30.207
HEY, GUYS.

12:30.291 --> 12:33.043
I'M BESSIE HIGGENBOTTOM,
HONEYBEE TROOP 828.

12:33.127 --> 12:34.837
[buzzing]

12:34.920 --> 12:36.338
LISTEN, HERE'S THE SKINNY.

12:36.422 --> 12:37.214
BEST-CASE SCENARIO,
YOU'RE ABOUT TO BE EVICTED.

12:37.298 --> 12:39.758
[flames whooshing]

12:39.842 --> 12:42.219
PERHAPS I CAN HELP.

12:42.303 --> 12:42.928
[buzzing]

12:43.012 --> 12:45.181
THIS CASA COULD BE <i> SU</i> CASA

12:45.264 --> 12:46.724
FOR JUST ONE HARVEST OF HONEY.

12:46.807 --> 12:47.558
[buzzing]

12:47.641 --> 12:50.227
NO, NO, NO, NO,
NOT FOR PROFIT.

12:50.311 --> 12:51.520
IT'S STRICTLY SO I CAN EARN

12:51.604 --> 12:53.606
THE EVER-ELUSIVE
BEEKEEPING BADGE.

12:53.689 --> 12:55.024
SO WHAT DO YOU SAY?

12:55.107 --> 12:57.359
I STING YOUR BACK,
YOU STING MINE?

12:57.443 --> 13:00.154
[bees buzzing]

13:00.237 --> 13:01.906
HEY EVERYBODY!

13:01.989 --> 13:04.033
JUST WANNA MAKE
A QUICK ANNOUNCEMENT.

13:04.116 --> 13:07.828
WE'RE ON TRACK TO OUR GOAL
OF 1,000 GALLONS OF HONEY,

13:07.912 --> 13:12.124
SO I AM PLEASED TO INTRODUCE
CASUAL FRIDAYS.

13:12.208 --> 13:14.210
TIME TO BUST OUT
THOSE HAWAIIAN SHIRTS

13:14.293 --> 13:16.003
AT THE BACK OF YOUR CLOSETS.

13:16.086 --> 13:17.546
I'M LOOKING AT YOU, ALEX!

13:17.630 --> 13:20.424
[laughs]

13:20.508 --> 13:23.552
- OKAY, HAPPY, HERE'S HOPING
FOR SOME BOLOGNA.

13:23.636 --> 13:25.596
IF IT'S FRESH, TWO FOR ME,
ONE FOR YOU.

13:25.679 --> 13:27.932
IF IT'S MOLDY, TWO FOR YOU,
ONE FOR ME.

13:28.015 --> 13:29.099
- [barks happily]

13:30.184 --> 13:31.560
- [gasps]

13:31.644 --> 13:33.187
SHANGRI-LA.

13:33.270 --> 13:35.064
[applause]

13:35.147 --> 13:36.106
I KNOW!

13:37.900 --> 13:43.072
POTATO SALAD, ROAST CHICKEN,
CORN ON THE COB,

13:43.155 --> 13:46.075
BROWNIES WITH SUGAR!

13:46.158 --> 13:48.869
IT'S LIKE THANKSGIVING
WITHOUT THE BORING PILGRIMS!

13:49.495 --> 13:52.248
[bees buzzing]

13:52.331 --> 13:53.165
[screaming]

13:53.249 --> 13:56.335
- GUYS, GUYS,
THIS IS A COMPANY PICNIC

13:56.418 --> 13:58.045
TO CELEBRATE THE HALFWAY
TO HARVEST MARK.

13:58.128 --> 13:59.255
- HUH?

13:59.338 --> 14:00.297
- DID WE SEND THE MEMO?

14:01.340 --> 14:02.591
UGH, WE FORGOT.

14:02.675 --> 14:03.842
I'VE GONE INTO THE HONEY
BUSINESS.

14:03.926 --> 14:07.137
IT'S FOR THE EVER-ELUSIVE
BEEKEEPING BADGE.

14:07.221 --> 14:09.974
ANYWAY, YOU'RE WELCOME TO STAY.

14:10.057 --> 14:12.518
[bees buzzing]

14:13.561 --> 14:16.772
- [whimpering]

14:16.855 --> 14:18.816
- OOH, HAPPY,
COULD YOU PLEASE WAIT

14:18.899 --> 14:20.192
UNTIL THE EMPLOYEES
HAVE EATEN FIRST?

14:20.276 --> 14:22.861
THANKS.

14:22.945 --> 14:24.905
[bees buzzing]

14:32.037 --> 14:34.373
- [yawns]

14:34.456 --> 14:36.458
[gasps]

14:36.542 --> 14:39.336
[bees buzzing]

14:41.547 --> 14:44.508
[screaming]

14:45.718 --> 14:47.469
- OH, YOU WOKE THEM UP.

14:47.553 --> 14:49.597
THIS IS MY NEW ON-SITE
DAYCARE CENTER.

14:49.680 --> 14:50.347
YOU'RE GONNA BUNK WITH HAPPY.

14:50.431 --> 14:53.559
- B-B-B-B-B-BU--

14:53.642 --> 14:56.145
- MR. PANTS CAN COME TOO.

14:56.604 --> 15:00.149
[tools whirring]

15:05.029 --> 15:06.322
KEEP IT FLOWIN', GUYS.

15:06.405 --> 15:07.781
HONEY DOESN'T SLEEP.

15:07.865 --> 15:09.366
- [growling]

15:09.450 --> 15:10.367
- HAPPY, DO SOMETHING.

15:10.451 --> 15:13.537
MR. PANTS CAN'T SLEEP.

15:13.621 --> 15:16.624
[banging]

15:24.673 --> 15:27.635
[rooster crowing]

15:27.718 --> 15:29.219
[groaning]

15:29.303 --> 15:31.513
[gasps]

15:31.597 --> 15:33.223
[screaming]

15:33.307 --> 15:35.225
MR. PANTS!

15:37.895 --> 15:39.647
MR. PANTS!

15:39.730 --> 15:45.611
HE NEVER GOT TO SEE SPAIN!

15:45.694 --> 15:48.697
[knocking at door]

15:48.781 --> 15:50.032
- HI, GUYS.

15:50.115 --> 15:51.367
LISTEN, I'M NOT ACCEPTING
ANYMORE APPLICATIONS

15:51.450 --> 15:53.535
AT THIS TIME.

15:53.619 --> 15:56.622
- [angry barking]

15:59.833 --> 16:00.876
- HAPPY, I'VE GOT THIS.

16:00.959 --> 16:04.129
YOUR STUPID BEES
ATE ALL OUR FOOD,

16:04.213 --> 16:07.424
REPEATEDLY STUNG US,
AND DROWNED MR. PANTS!

16:07.508 --> 16:09.843
HAPPY HAD TO GIVE HIM
MOUTH-TO-MOUTH!

16:09.927 --> 16:12.179
- [hacking and retching]

16:12.262 --> 16:13.722
- ALL YOU CARE ABOUT
IS THAT STUPID

16:13.806 --> 16:16.392
EVER-ELUSIVE BEEKEEPING BADGE!

16:16.475 --> 16:18.394
- UGH, I CANT BELIEVE
WHAT I'M HEARING.

16:18.477 --> 16:21.271
DON'T YOU WANT ME TO COLLECT
EVERY SINGLE HONEYBEE BADGE?

16:21.355 --> 16:22.940
DON'T YOU WANT ME TO BECOME
THE MIGHTY BEE?

16:23.023 --> 16:24.650
DON'T YOU WANT ME
TO OVERACHIEVE?

16:24.733 --> 16:26.860
[together]
MEH.

16:26.944 --> 16:29.947
- WELL, THANK YOU
FOR YOUR HONESTY.

16:30.030 --> 16:31.365
FROM NOW ON,

16:31.448 --> 16:32.741
MY BEES AND I WILL STAY
ON OUR SIDE OF THE PROPERTY,

16:32.825 --> 16:35.577
AND YOU'LL STAY ON YOURS.

16:35.661 --> 16:38.247
CONSIDER THIS A FEUD.

16:38.330 --> 16:40.207
WHAT?

16:40.290 --> 16:41.583
NOT CLEAR ENOUGH?

16:41.667 --> 16:42.835
BUZZ, BUZZ, BUZZ, BUZZ.

16:42.918 --> 16:44.920
YOU'RE STUNG!
BUZZ, BUZZ, BUZZ.

16:45.003 --> 16:45.546
THIS IS ME STINGING YOU.

16:45.629 --> 16:47.423
OH, FORGET IT!

16:47.506 --> 16:49.758
IT'S A BEE THING.

16:49.842 --> 16:53.929
[door slams]

16:54.012 --> 16:55.472
I LOVE YOU GUYS TOO!

16:55.556 --> 16:58.475
[bees buzzing]

16:58.559 --> 16:59.977
YOUR QUEEN?

17:00.060 --> 17:01.979
IT WOULD BE MY HONOR.

17:02.062 --> 17:04.021
[bees buzzing]

17:19.579 --> 17:21.123
crash!

17:21.205 --> 17:23.791
TASTES...

17:23.876 --> 17:24.710
READY!

17:24.792 --> 17:25.794
LET'S GO.

17:25.877 --> 17:28.589
[bees buzzing]

17:28.672 --> 17:30.382
[doorbell rings]

17:30.466 --> 17:32.593
- [screaming]

17:32.676 --> 17:34.470
PLEASE, DON'T STING!

17:34.553 --> 17:36.555
SOME OF MY BEST FRIENDS
ARE BEES.

17:36.638 --> 17:39.892
- [screaming]

17:39.975 --> 17:42.936
MRS. GIBBONS, I PRESENT TO YOU

17:43.020 --> 17:46.315
ONE COMPLETE HONEY HARVEST
JARRED AND LABELED,

17:46.398 --> 17:49.818
AS REQUIRED FOR THE EVER-ELUSIVE
BEEKEEPING BADGE.

17:49.902 --> 17:53.238
- WILL YOU ASK THEM TO SPARE ME?

17:53.322 --> 17:54.448
[teeth chattering]

17:54.531 --> 17:55.616
- OH, THAT?

17:55.699 --> 17:58.118
THAT'S JUST BEE HUMOR.

17:58.202 --> 17:59.161
IT'S VERY DARK.

17:59.244 --> 17:59.870
YOU GET USED TO IT.

17:59.953 --> 18:02.831
- JUST TAKE IT, JUST TAKE IT!

18:02.915 --> 18:04.583
[bees buzzing]

18:10.756 --> 18:12.716
- I CAN'T BELIEVE IT,

18:12.800 --> 18:16.512
THE EVER-ELUSIVE
BEEKEEPING BADGE.

18:16.595 --> 18:18.764
[sighs]

18:18.847 --> 18:21.141
ALL RIGHT, GUYS,
THAT'S A WRAP ON THE HONEYBEES.

18:21.225 --> 18:23.894
I CAN'T THANK YOU ENOUGH
FOR ALL YOUR HARD WORK.

18:23.977 --> 18:25.354
IT'S BEEN A GREAT WEEK.

18:25.437 --> 18:26.688
AND OF COURSE,

18:26.772 --> 18:28.398
I'M MORE THAN HAPPY
TO WRITE EACH OF YOU

18:28.482 --> 18:31.777
AN ENTHUSIASTIC LETTER
OF RECOMMENDATION.

18:31.860 --> 18:33.028
OH.

18:33.111 --> 18:35.697
HERE'S HOW A BADGE MISSION
WORKS, GUYS.

18:35.781 --> 18:37.366
WE DO THE WORK
TO EARN THE BADGE.

18:37.449 --> 18:39.076
I RECEIVE SAID BADGE,

18:39.159 --> 18:41.036
AND THEN ITS TIME TO MOVE ON
TO THE NEXT ACHIEVEMENT.

18:41.119 --> 18:41.995
SEE?

18:42.079 --> 18:42.955
[bees buzzing]

18:43.038 --> 18:44.122
OR NOT.

18:46.250 --> 18:50.879
MM, THE FIRST TEN MOUTHFULS
WERE REALLY GOOD.

18:50.963 --> 18:53.549
NOW HOW ABOUT LITTLE BREAK?

18:53.632 --> 18:56.593
[bees buzzing]

18:58.011 --> 18:58.720
OH, AH.

18:58.804 --> 19:01.598
LOVE YOU TOO.

19:02.641 --> 19:06.436
- [angry barking]

19:21.243 --> 19:23.203
[tapping on glass]

19:26.748 --> 19:30.460
[confused growling]

19:38.802 --> 19:39.595
- OW.

19:39.678 --> 19:41.555
YOU'RE RIGHT.

19:41.638 --> 19:42.848
IT IS AN EXCELLENT HAIR PRODUCT.

19:42.931 --> 19:44.683
THIS WILL HOLD ALL DAY.

19:44.766 --> 19:46.852
[bees buzzing]

19:46.935 --> 19:48.937
BUT MAYBE WE NEED
SOME CREAM RINSE.

19:49.021 --> 19:53.108
SHOULD BE SOME IN THE CABINETS.

19:57.696 --> 20:00.157
[toilet flushing]

20:00.240 --> 20:02.201
- OOH, I WASN'T EXPECTING THAT.

20:02.284 --> 20:05.454
[strange rattling]

20:05.537 --> 20:08.665
HMM, I NEVER NOTICED
THIS SECOND TOILET BEFORE.

20:08.749 --> 20:10.417
EW.

20:10.500 --> 20:12.419
WHO ATE A HONEY JAR?

20:12.502 --> 20:12.753
[gasps]

20:12.836 --> 20:14.796
HAPPY!

20:14.880 --> 20:15.505
- [grunts]

20:15.589 --> 20:17.674
- IT'S A MESSAGE FROM BESSIE.

20:17.758 --> 20:20.802
- [sighs]

20:20.886 --> 20:22.888
[gasps and whimpers]

20:22.971 --> 20:26.141
"DEAR BEN AND HAPPY,
I'M VERY, VERY SORRY.

20:26.224 --> 20:28.310
"NOW THAT THAT'S
OUT OF THE WAY,

20:28.393 --> 20:29.269
"THEY'VE GOT ME!

20:29.353 --> 20:29.978
"I'M A PRISONER IN MY OWN HIVE.

20:30.062 --> 20:31.813
"THEY'VE MADE ME THEIR QUEEN.

20:31.897 --> 20:32.981
"IT'S A PRETTY BIG HONOR,

20:33.065 --> 20:34.483
"BUT THE ONLY WAY
THEY'LL LET ME GO

20:34.566 --> 20:36.360
"IS IF I AM FELLED AND REPLACED
BY ANOTHER QUEEN BEE.

20:36.443 --> 20:37.986
THAT'S WHERE YOU GUYS COME IN."

20:38.070 --> 20:39.738
- WELL THAT'S
ALL FINE AND DANDY,

20:39.821 --> 20:44.034
BUT WHERE ARE WE GONNA GET
ANOTHER QUEEN BEE?

20:46.995 --> 20:50.666
IT KEEPS RIDING UP.

20:50.749 --> 20:52.793
- [laughs]

20:52.876 --> 20:55.337
[lock clicking]

20:59.299 --> 21:02.678
[bees buzzing]

21:02.761 --> 21:03.720
- [grunting]

21:03.804 --> 21:04.846
UGH.

21:04.930 --> 21:05.847
[gasps]

21:05.931 --> 21:07.849
[guns clicking]

21:07.933 --> 21:11.687
[water gushing]

21:13.438 --> 21:17.234
- THIS HIVE'S ONLY BIG ENOUGH
FOR ONE QUEEN,

21:17.317 --> 21:18.735
AND YOU'RE LOOKIN' AT HIM!

21:18.819 --> 21:20.779
- HOORAY!

21:20.862 --> 21:23.448
OH, I MEAN,
NO!

21:23.532 --> 21:24.866
BOO!

21:24.950 --> 21:29.454
QUEEN BEN,
HOW DARE YOU CHALLENGE ME?

21:29.538 --> 21:31.498
[bees buzzing]

21:33.792 --> 21:35.961
[water gushing]

21:36.044 --> 21:36.795
STAND DOWN, SWARM.

21:36.878 --> 21:40.966
THIS IS BETWEEN QUEENS.

21:42.384 --> 21:43.385
WAY TO SELL IT.

21:43.468 --> 21:45.387
THRUST, PARRY,

21:45.470 --> 21:47.264
TURN!

21:47.347 --> 21:48.640
HIYA!

21:48.724 --> 21:51.268
OOF!

21:51.351 --> 21:53.311
[bees buzzing]

21:55.564 --> 21:57.482
[explosion]

22:02.070 --> 22:02.988
I'M HIT!

22:03.071 --> 22:03.947
I'M HIT!

22:04.031 --> 22:05.073
THIS IS IT.

22:05.157 --> 22:07.492
CHECKMATE.

22:07.576 --> 22:09.286
I REGRET NOTHING.

22:09.369 --> 22:10.412
- YES!

22:10.495 --> 22:12.080
QUEEN ME!

22:12.164 --> 22:15.167
[triumphant music]

22:15.250 --> 22:22.257
♪ ♪

22:30.515 --> 22:32.726
THEY'RE NOT COMING BACK,
ARE THEY?

